<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/51716760-l-a"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_100x100-6433b08cbe793211f55e184d39e84c4d.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/51716760-l-a">Léa</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think popol was a child invented by momo&apos;s father to make momo feel like he was not doing things the right way. For my part I think popol was just a<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think popol was a child invented by momo's father to make momo feel like he was not doing things the right way. For my part I think popol was just a part of momo's father imagination, a character used by his father to represent people in general and to deliverate a message to his son. I don't think Momo's father did really love him and that's why he used Popol, to make his son understand he was not perfect but that someone else was, to make momo think he was not a good boy.<br /><br />(I'm not sure it's really clear but I hope so haha')<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
