        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2375267998" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5264847269709702749"><b>2.5 stars rounded up to 3!</b><br/><br/>I had this book in my bookshelf for quite a while now - I bought it on a flea market and I was really looking forward to reading it. I somehow felt <b>mesmerized by the beautiful title</b> and I might have had too high expectations regarding this book. <b>I wanted to love it!</b> And it was a good book, it is special, so very different from what I usually read and I felt entertained, but it was <b>not as perfect as I wanted it to be</b>! It touched so many topics in just a few pages and I k</span>
  <span id="freeText5264847269709702749" style="display:none"><b>2.5 stars rounded up to 3!</b><br /><br />I had this book in my bookshelf for quite a while now - I bought it on a flea market and I was really looking forward to reading it. I somehow felt <b>mesmerized by the beautiful title</b> and I might have had too high expectations regarding this book. <b>I wanted to love it!</b> And it was a good book, it is special, so very different from what I usually read and I felt entertained, but it was <b>not as perfect as I wanted it to be</b>! It touched so many topics in just a few pages and I kept thinking about them, while new things happened and I was not really into the story due to the strange pace. I did love the character and the way they interacted!</span>
  <a data-text-id="5264847269709702749" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
