<div id="review_1148543438" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1148543438" />
    <a title="Mark Bandeira" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/36665270-mark-bandeira"><img alt="Mark Bandeira" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1417080991p2/36665270.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1148543438?book_show_action=true">Dec 31, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mark Bandeira" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mark Bandeira" href="/user/show/36665270-mark-bandeira">Mark Bandeira</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9782210754676" href="/book/show/1016601.Monsieur_Ibrahim_Et_Les_Fleurs_Du_Coran">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1148543438" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15821070596679761041">&quot;M. Ibrahim et les Fleurs du Coran&quot; is one of those stories that MUST be read by everyone. It touches on so many aspects of human life, but I would say that the main ones are prejudice and family relations. I came out with the following lesson: we are whom we choose to be.</span>
  <span id="freeText15821070596679761041" style="display:none">"M. Ibrahim et les Fleurs du Coran" is one of those stories that MUST be read by everyone. It touches on so many aspects of human life, but I would say that the main ones are prejudice and family relations. I came out with the following lesson: we are whom we choose to be.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15821070596679761041" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


